verses.text:
On that day they read in the book of Moses in the hearing of the people;
and it was found written in it that an Ammonite and a Moabite should not enter into the assembly of God
forever,

I made treasurers over the treasuries, Shelemiah the priest, and Zadok
the scribe, and of the Levites, Pedaiah: and next to them was Hanan the son of Zaccur, the son of Mattaniah;
for they were counted faithful, and their business was to distribute to their brothers.
